    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos(v1) / wp.cos((v2 + 0.53 + tmp + 0.38)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.80)
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.87 + v1 + 0.90)) + 0.17)
    v2 = 0.29
    tmp = v1
    tmp = 0.13
    v0 = ((tmp + wp.abs(v2 + 0.68)) - wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.20)))
    v0 = 0.56
    data[tid] = v0
